::Hevn::
       "Oh Maxima, don't look so glum.  It doesn't suit you at all." *tsk tsk 
tsk* He looks over to the new Decepticons.  "Well, my name is Hevngjerrig.  
But everyone who can't remember or pronounce that calls me Hevn."  He smiles 
amicably as he glances at the obviously unhappy Maxima.  "Come on Maxima, I want 
to see a smile."
